snippet: LSU running back Leonard Fournette will sit out the 19th-ranked Tigers' matchup with No. 15 Louisville in the Citrus Bowl, a decision that ends his highlight-filled collegiate career....
lead_paragraph: LSU running back Leonard Fournette will sit out the 19th-ranked Tigers' matchup with No. 15 Louisville in the Citrus Bowl, a decision that ends his highlight-filled collegiate career.
